968
01:39:46,146 --> 01:39:48,273
Help!

969
01:39:48,449 --> 01:39:52,078
- Let us in!
- Who are you kidding?

970
01:40:02,696 --> 01:40:07,360
What are you doing?
The cat don't like visitors.

971
01:40:16,910 --> 01:40:20,869
They're going to get us. Where's Sam?

972
01:40:21,048 --> 01:40:24,916
- lt looks like the bitch just left.
- l'll check downstairs.

973
01:40:36,330 --> 01:40:37,729
Carl?

974
01:41:27,781 --> 01:41:29,009
Willie!

975
01:41:38,325 --> 01:41:41,226
You've got a serious problem, man.

976
01:42:02,950 --> 01:42:06,010
Help me! Help!

977
01:43:02,476 --> 01:43:04,774
That dude is dead.

978
01:43:09,750 --> 01:43:11,217
You're dead, Willie.

979
01:43:41,315 --> 01:43:44,876
Help me!

980
01:44:05,606 --> 01:44:07,938
Tell the driver to hurry.

981
01:44:08,108 --> 01:44:13,171
- Can you step on it, please.
- l'm driving as fast as l can.

982
01:44:20,821 --> 01:44:22,015
Problems?

983
01:44:30,097 --> 01:44:32,930
- Carl, is that you?
- lt's me, Oda Mae.

984
01:44:33,100 --> 01:44:38,470
l know what you think of me, but we've
got to talk. You are in serious danger.

985
01:44:39,206 --> 01:44:43,267
- l've got Sam here with me.
- Get the hell out of here!

986
01:44:43,443 --> 01:44:46,310
- lm calling the police!
- Good. Tell her to do it!

987
01:44:46,480 --> 01:44:51,474
Fine. We want you to call the police.
But you´ve got to let us in.

988
01:44:52,452 --> 01:44:56,889
Don't you get it? Sam wasn't
accidentally killed, he was murdered.

989
01:44:57,057 --> 01:44:59,855
He found out
that Carl was laundering money.

990
01:45:00,027 --> 01:45:02,928
Carl is dangerous. He tried to kill me.

991
01:45:03,096 --> 01:45:07,430
He's going to try to kill you, too.
You are in deep, deep trouble.

992
01:45:07,601 --> 01:45:13,062
Why are you doing this to me?
Do you hear me?

993
01:45:13,240 --> 01:45:17,574
Why are you doing this to me?

994
01:45:18,478 --> 01:45:24,041
Oda Mae. Tell her she's wearing
the shirt that l spilt the margarita on,

995
01:45:24,217 --> 01:45:27,243
and the earrings
l gave her for Christmas.

996
01:45:27,421 --> 01:45:31,380
Sam says you're wearing the shirt
he spilt the margarita on,

997
01:45:31,558 --> 01:45:34,959
and the earrings
he gave you for Christmas.

998
01:45:40,267 --> 01:45:43,668
Don't you see?
l'm not a fake! Not about this.

999
01:45:49,176 --> 01:45:51,474
- Give me a penny.
- What?

1000
01:45:51,645 --> 01:45:57,982
- Push a penny under the door, now!
- What are you talking about?

1001
01:46:34,454 --> 01:46:38,220
- Tell her it's for luck.
- Sam says it's for luck.

1002
01:47:14,361 --> 01:47:16,420
Between Green and Mercer on Prince.

1003
01:47:16,596 --> 01:47:19,793
lt's the grey building
across from the post office.

1004
01:47:19,966 --> 01:47:24,130
Thanks, Sergeant. Please hurry!
We'll be waiting.

1005
01:47:24,304 --> 01:47:27,205
- They're on their way.
- Good.

1006
01:47:28,742 --> 01:47:32,439
- What do we do now?
- Just wait.

1007
01:47:42,489 --> 01:47:45,458
ls Sam here?

1008
01:47:45,625 --> 01:47:48,093
Sam?

1009
01:47:48,261 --> 01:47:51,321
l'm sitting beside her.

1010
01:47:51,498 --> 01:47:54,433
He's sitting right beside you.

1011
01:48:03,610 --> 01:48:05,942
Sam, can you feel me?

1012
01:48:07,280 --> 01:48:09,748
With all my heart.

1013
01:48:09,916 --> 01:48:12,749
He says with all his heart.

1014
01:48:24,498 --> 01:48:28,901
l'd give anything
if l could just touch you once more.

1015
01:48:31,938 --> 01:48:35,533
He says he wishes he was alive again,
so he could touch you.

1016
01:48:39,079 --> 01:48:40,546
Me, too.

1017
01:48:57,430 --> 01:49:01,389
OK. Look - you can use me.

1018
01:49:02,602 --> 01:49:05,230
- Use you?
- Use my body.

1019
01:49:05,405 --> 01:49:08,465
- Use your body?
- Quick, before l change my mind.

1020
01:52:17,497 --> 01:52:20,159
- Molly, are you home?
- Carl.

1021
01:52:21,568 --> 01:52:24,036
- Molly!
- Fire escape.

1022
01:52:30,977 --> 01:52:32,877
What's happening to me?

1023
01:52:36,850 --> 01:52:40,445
Molly?

1024
01:52:49,429 --> 01:52:51,021
Molly!

1025
01:53:06,079 --> 01:53:07,706
Come on!

1026
01:53:10,717 --> 01:53:12,048
Look!

1027
01:53:13,353 --> 01:53:14,786
Let's go!

1028
01:53:25,398 --> 01:53:30,062
- Molly!
- Get away from us, Carl!

1029
01:53:32,405 --> 01:53:34,464
- Molly!
- You're just a liar.

1030
01:53:34,641 --> 01:53:38,133
This woman's a thief.
She's a con artist.

1031
01:53:38,311 --> 01:53:40,836
Why are you doing this?

1032
01:53:42,882 --> 01:53:45,009
Stop!

1033
01:53:45,185 --> 01:53:47,983
Get away from us.
l've called the police.

1034
01:53:57,797 --> 01:54:00,095
Shit!

1035
01:54:01,601 --> 01:54:04,627
- Carl, why are you doing this?
- She's a thief!

1036
01:54:07,340 --> 01:54:11,470
Just give me the cheque!

1037
01:54:18,484 --> 01:54:20,816
Stay out of this, Molly!

1038
01:54:20,987 --> 01:54:25,151
Get off me!

1039
01:54:28,962 --> 01:54:30,953
Where is it?

1040
01:54:31,130 --> 01:54:34,122
- Where is it, goddammit?
- l gave it away.

1041
01:54:34,300 --> 01:54:38,828
You're lying to me.
Don't lie to me, goddammit.

1042
01:54:41,074 --> 01:54:42,769
The cheque!

1043
01:54:55,088 --> 01:54:58,819
l'll kill her, Sam.
l swear to God, l'll kill her!

1044
01:55:08,468 --> 01:55:11,369
Just give me the cheque, Sam.

1045
01:55:11,537 --> 01:55:17,169
l promise you l'll let her go
if you just give it to me.

1046
01:56:38,758 --> 01:56:40,191
Sam?

1047
01:56:42,595 --> 01:56:44,256
Oh, Carl...

1048
01:56:44,430 --> 01:56:46,489
What?

1049
01:57:53,800 --> 01:57:56,291
Are you two all right?

1050
01:57:59,472 --> 01:58:01,770
Sam?

1051
01:58:03,509 --> 01:58:05,534
Molly?

1052
01:58:07,313 --> 01:58:09,713
l can hear you!

1053
01:58:45,351 --> 01:58:47,148
Oh, God!

1054
01:59:34,634 --> 01:59:36,261
Sam?

1055
01:59:37,036 --> 01:59:40,096
They're waiting for you.

1056
01:59:49,982 --> 01:59:53,145
l'll miss you.

1057
01:59:53,319 --> 01:59:55,116
Your mother'd be proud.

1058
01:59:55,988 --> 02:00:00,618
l'm going to miss you too, Sam.
You're all right!

1059
02:00:02,261 --> 02:00:04,354
Bye, Oda Mae.

1060
02:00:05,131 --> 02:00:07,497
Bye, Sam.

1061
02:00:29,355 --> 02:00:31,721
l love you, Molly.

1062
02:00:33,426 --> 02:00:35,394
l've always loved you.

1063
02:00:42,235 --> 02:00:44,703
Ditto.

1064
02:01:04,657 --> 02:01:07,558
lt's amazing, Molly.

1065
02:01:07,727 --> 02:01:11,857
The love inside - you take it with you.

1066
02:01:23,309 --> 02:01:25,300
See you.

1067
02:01:32,184 --> 02:01:34,209
See you.

1068
02:01:52,405 --> 02:01:53,633
Bye.

1069
02:06:31,784 --> 02:06:34,014
ENGLlSH

